reviewText: MIND ENLIGHTENMENT FOR FUTURE AS IN REVELATIONS

If you are Catholic and love The Blessed Mother DO NOT buy this over priced DVD!  This DVD is not a collection of Marys apparitions. This DVD contains some fast talking man who stares in the camera in a very creepy way using his interpretation of scripture to disprove the teachings of the Catholic church on Mary.  I threw the disc in the trash where it belongs.
received time and happy with book
